        },
        {
          "fact_id": "colorado-childcare-background-checks-2",
          "category": "background_checks",
          "text": "Colorado child care licensing — 32 Use of Reports and Records of Child Abuse or Neglect for Background and Employment Inquiries [Rev.",
          "citation": {
            "source": "Colorado 7 CCR 1-3.5 (SOS admin-code PDF)",
            "url": "https://www.sos.state.co.us/CCR/GenerateRulePdf.do?ruleVersionId=973",
            "agency": "Colorado 7 CCR 1-3.5 (SOS admin-code PDF)",
            "category": "background_checks",
            "tier": "tertiary",
            "retrieved_date": "2026-06-19"
          },
          "grade": {
            "status": "FOUND",
            "tier": "tertiary",
            "category": "background_checks"
          }
        },
        {
          "fact_id": "colorado-childcare-background-checks-3",
          "category": "background_checks",
          "text": "Colorado child care licensing — 9/1/06] A request to determine whether any owner, applicant, employee, licensee or resident of a licensed facility, or any supervisory employee of a guest care facility, was found to be responsible in a confirmed report of child abuse or neglect reported to the State Department’s automated system shall be directed to and be the responsibility of the State Department.",
          "citation": {
            "source": "Colorado 7 CCR 1-3.5 (SOS admin-code PDF)",
            "url": "https://www.sos.state.co.us/CCR/GenerateRulePdf.do?ruleVersionId=973",
            "agency": "Colorado 7 CCR 1-3.5 (SOS admin-code PDF)",
            "category": "background_checks",
            "tier": "tertiary",
            "retrieved_date": "2026-06-19"
          },
          "grade": {
            "status": "FOUND",
            "tier": "tertiary",
            "category": "background_checks"
          }
        },
        {
          "fact_id": "colorado-childcare-background-checks-4",
          "category": "background_checks",
          "text": "Colorado child care licensing — The State Department will inform the requesting party in writing of whether the individual has been confirmed to be responsible for an incident of child abuse or neglect.",
          "citation": {
            "source": "Colorado 7 CCR 1-3.5 (SOS admin-code PDF)",
            "url": "https://www.sos.state.co.us/CCR/GenerateRulePdf.do?ruleVersionId=973",
            "agency": "Colorado 7 CCR 1-3.5 (SOS admin-code PDF)",
            "category": "background_checks",
            "tier": "tertiary",
            "retrieved_date": "2026-06-19"
          },
          "grade": {
            "status": "FOUND",
            "tier": "tertiary",
            "category": "background_checks"
          }
        },
        {
          "fact_id": "colorado-childcare-background-checks-5",
          "category": "background_checks",
          "text": "Colorado child care licensing — If the result of the inquiry is that the individual has been confirmed as responsible for an incident of child abuse or neglect, the State Department shall provide the requesting party with information regarding the date of the reported incident, the type of abuse or neglect with the severity level, and the county department that confirmed the report.",
          "citation": {
            "source": "Colorado 7 CCR 1-3.5 (SOS admin-code PDF)",
            "url": "https://www.sos.state.co.us/CCR/GenerateRulePdf.do?ruleVersionId=973",
            "agency": "Colorado 7 CCR 1-3.5 (SOS admin-code PDF)",
            "category": "background_checks",
            "tier": "tertiary",
            "retrieved_date": "2026-06-19"
          },
          "grade": {
            "status": "FOUND",
            "tier": "tertiary",
            "category": "background_checks"
          }
        },
        {
          "fact_id": "colorado-childcare-background-checks-6",
          "category": "background_checks",
          "text": "Colorado child care licensing — If the result of the inquiry is that the individual has not been confirmed to be responsible for an incident of child abuse or neglect, the State Department shall notify the requesting party of this fact.",
          "citation": {
            "source": "Colorado 7 CCR 1-3.5 (SOS admin-code PDF)",
            "url": "https://www.sos.state.co.us/CCR/GenerateRulePdf.do?ruleVersionId=973",
